{"tid":830062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"威尼斯「禁坐令」對付粗魯遊客 地上坐臥罰款4580 下月投票立法","createTime":"2018-09-21T02:18:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T04:25:23.000Z","uid":150685,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"255b66d00f213f87af21f067d442c007da69382c","tid":830062,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T02:18:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20180921/s00060/b247e86cd5e2e3bf497c367e1568cc96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20180921%2Fs00060%2Fb247e86cd5e2e3bf497c367e1568cc96.jpg&h=9b86f2ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】意大利「水都」威尼斯每日平均接待約6萬名遊客，為應付部分旅客的粗魯行為，市長提出立法禁止人們在地上坐臥，違者會被罰款50至500歐元（約458至4584港元）。威尼斯此前亦立法禁止多種行為，有民間組織批評政策太嚴，動輒得咎。<br />\n<br />\n威尼斯一直希望處理大批旅客來訪所造成的問題，禁止坐或躺在地上的提案由市長布魯尼亞羅（Luigi Brugnaro）提出。在這之前，市內聖馬可廣場周圍的紀念碑台階和門廊早已禁止坐臥。英國《衛報》指當局在遠離旅遊熱點地方劃有野餐及坐下的範圍，但鮮為人注意。<br />\n<br />\n新法案預計10月在市議會投票，左翼政黨「五星運動」及居民組織都反對立法。一個居民組織的負責人加斯帕里內蒂（Marco Gasparinetti）說：「威尼斯有一張長長的禁令清單，你什麼都不能做。」他又指當局若要有效執法，就需要增聘5000人。<br />\n<br />\n「禮儀天使」巡邏助守規<br />\n<br />\n坐或躺在地上並非威尼斯政府首項禁止的行為，當局早已禁止在運河中浸腳與游泳、在階梯或散步時進食等。去年威尼斯政府亦發起運動，列出一系列禁止的事項，如未經許可在街頭表演、野餐都會被罰款。<br />\n<br />\n每年夏季都會有一班「禮儀天使」（angels of decorum）於威尼斯的主要旅遊熱點巡邏，確保遊客守法。威尼斯旅遊部門負責人馬爾在今年7月曾表示，這些禮儀規定無意把特定群體視為罪犯，而是希望人們尊重威尼斯。<br />\n<br />\n（衛報/獨立報）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180921/s00014/1537467447072\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180921%2Fs00014%2F1537467447072&d=SYfG%2FrpWfShsoGytOeV0sTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=c7257558\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180921%2Fs00014%2F1537467447072&h=e3bdb633\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180921/s00014/1537467447072</a>"},{"pid":"be5952fa0cccb443a6d276cb8987ba310399d3a0","tid":830062,"uid":150685,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T02:18:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://image.cache.storm.mg/styles/smg-800x533-fp/s3/media/image/2018/01/24/20180124-115417_U3927_M373068_efaf.jpg?itok=h_aU8Euc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.cache.storm.mg%2Fstyles%2Fsmg-800x533-fp%2Fs3%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2018%2F01%2F24%2F20180124-115417_U3927_M373068_efaf.jpg%3Fitok%3Dh_aU8Euc&h=911c7bd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n支持香港有禁踎令 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2df5b85f06208f441adce68df0cf682dab819c68","tid":830062,"uid":43130,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T02:21:26.000Z","msg":"搞掂啲賊先啦，佢老味"},{"pid":"5e4a621318773db786f7b1c3ee6a575c26086aee","tid":830062,"uid":54884,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T03:18:16.000Z","msg":"外國人先最鍾意咁樣坐"},{"pid":"81d535b6f1537c511e3ec1e8abeca90a378a73de","tid":830062,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T03:23:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5324cfa58c93a21aedfd30e5dcc8a047d85ca869","tid":830062,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T03:25:54.000Z","msg":"好彩我地中國人鍾意踎唔鍾意坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46e257ed3eae8ee7d5dcefc269cdcc5787030f17","tid":830062,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5324cfa58c93a21aedfd30e5dcc8a047d85ca869","tid":830062,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T03:25:54.000Z","msg":"好彩我地中國人鍾意踎唔鍾意坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T03:47:15.000Z","msg":"更加影響市容，見到就唔開胃 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"742ae6698b6ada38b4733b487f8e5ae0fdff7d85"